import React from 'react';

import { 
    Col,
    Form,
    Button
} from 'react-bootstrap';
  


// import { Container } from './styles';

export default function Registro() {
  return (
    <>
        <Form>
            <Form.Row>
                <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="Idoso">
                    <Form.Label>Idoso</Form.Label>
                    <Form.Control type="idoso" placeholder="Idoso" />
                </Form.Group>

                <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="Estudantes">
                    <Form.Label>Password</Form.Label>
                    <Form.Control type="estudantes" placeholder="Estudantes" />
                </Form.Group>
            </Form.Row>

            <Form.Group controlId="Internet">
                <Form.Label>Internet</Form.Label>
                <Form.Control placeholder="internet" />
            </Form.Group>

            <Form.Row>
                <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="Normal">
                <Form.Label>Normal</Form.Label>
            <Form.Control placeholder="Normal" />
            </Form.Group>

            <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="formGridState">
            <Form.Label>Horarios</Form.Label>
            <Form.Control as="select">
                <option>Selecionar</option>
                <option>04:00</option>
                <option>06:00</option>
                <option>07:00</option>
                <option>08:00</option>
                <option>10:30</option>
                <option></option>
            </Form.Control>
            </Form.Group>

                <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="formGridZip">
                <Form.Label>Zip</Form.Label>
                <Form.Control />
                </Form.Group>
            </Form.Row>

            <Button variant="primary" type="submit">
                Submit
            </Button>
        </Form>
   </>
  );
}
